<html lang='en'>
    <head>
        <meta charset='UTF-8' />
        <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
        <title>Reset Your Password</title>
        <style>
            body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6; color: #2d3748; margin: 0; padding: 0;
            background-color: #f7fafc; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin:
            40px auto; padding: 30px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius:
            12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .header {
            text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; } .logo { max-width: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 20px; } h1 { color: #1a365d; font-size: 24px; margin:
            0; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; }
            .content { padding: 20px 0; } .otp-container { text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px; } .otp-code { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 4px; color: #2b6cb0; padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #ebf8ff; border-radius: 6px; border: 2px solid
            #bee3f8; } .expires-text { color: #718096; font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px; } .footer { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e2e8f0; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096; } .security-notice { margin-top: 20px; padding:
            15px; background-color: #fff5f5; border-left: 4px solid #fc8181;
            color: #c53030; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 4px; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class='container'>
            <div class='header'>
                <img
                    src='http://localhost:5555/assets/images/Logo.png'
                    alt='BOM-Startup'
                    class='logo'
                />
                <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
            </div>

            <div class='content'>
                <p>Hello!</p>
                <p>We received a request to reset your password. To proceed with
                    the password reset, please use the verification code below:</p>

                <div class='otp-container'>
                    <div class='otp-code'>{{otp}}</div>
                    <p class='expires-text'>This code will expire in 15 minutes
                        for your security</p>
                </div>

                <p>To reset your password:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Enter this verification code on the password reset page</li>
                    <li>Create a new, strong password that you haven't used
                        before</li>
                    <li>Make sure to save your new password in a secure location</li>
                </ol>

                <div class='security-notice'>
                    <strong>Security Notice:</strong>
                    If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore
                    this email and ensure your account is secure by:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Checking your account activity</li>
                        <li>Updating your security settings</li>
                        <li>Contacting our support team if you notice any
                            suspicious activity</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class='footer'>
                <p>Â© 2025 BOM-Startup. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>For security reasons, please do not reply to this email.
                    Contact our support team if you need assistance.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>